36
00:04:28,489 --> 00:04:30,789
I like him.

37
00:04:31,370 --> 00:04:34,569
Those who don't flatter people

38
00:04:35,049 --> 00:04:39,030
are honest in their private time.

39
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:49,090
[Jiangning]

40
00:04:55,890 --> 00:04:59,649
In the fifth year of Jinghan, Jing arose

41
00:04:59,649 --> 00:05:04,768
and its Emperor envied the yearly tribute Wu gave to Liang.
[Jingliang Border]

42
00:05:04,768 --> 00:05:07,270
Jing challenged Liang,

43
00:05:07,270 --> 00:05:11,810
wishing to colonize Wu after conquering Liang.

44
00:05:11,810 --> 00:05:15,929
During the war, many people died in the north.

45
00:05:15,929 --> 00:05:19,029
People led a miserable life.

46
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:46,050
[Wudu Region]

47
00:05:48,210 --> 00:05:49,409
Jing Empire has arisen.

48
00:05:49,409 --> 00:05:50,650
