in the agreement with the Liang Empire can be canceled.

56
00:06:08,489 --> 00:06:12,020
We can decide after the war.
[Minister of the Ministry of Justice of the Wu Dynasty: Liang Qian Zhong]

57
00:06:12,020 --> 00:06:15,510
[Heaven and Earth to deliver peace]

58
00:06:15,510 --> 00:06:16,609
I second this.

59
00:06:16,609 --> 00:06:20,550
We should also send troops to the north border for defense.
[Left Prime Minister of Wu Dynasty: Li Gang]

60
00:06:20,550 --> 00:06:22,968
It would stop soldiers from the Liang Empire

61
00:06:22,968 --> 00:06:25,669
and avoid being involved in the war.

62
00:06:25,669 --> 00:06:27,970
Short sighted.

63
00:06:30,169 --> 00:06:31,569
Your Majesty,

64
00:06:31,569 --> 00:06:33,829
now in the war between Jing and Liang,

65
00:06:33,829 --> 00:06:35,608
Jing Empire is bound to win.

66
00:06:35,608 --> 00:06:38,809
In my opinion, the tribute or

67
00:06:38,809 --> 00:06:40,889
defense isn't the most important.

68
00:06:40,889 --> 00:06:43,190
We should attack the north.

69
00:06:43,190 --> 00:06:45,810
When the two are at war,

70
00:06:45,810 --> 00:06:47,270
we can take advantage of them

71
00:06:47,270 --> 00:06:49,889
and get back the six cities

72
00:06:49,889 --> 00:06:51,949
colonized by Liang Empire four years ago.

73
00:06:51,949 --> 00:06:53,649
Jing Empire is ambitious.

74
00:06:53,649 --> 00:06:55,349
If we let it go,

75
00:06:55,349 --> 00:06:59,609
we will be colonized one day.

76
