77
00:07:11,809 --> 00:07:14,150
Who can tell me

78
00:07:14,150 --> 00:07:18,529
what kind of a man the King of Jing is?

79
00:07:18,529 --> 00:07:20,470
I never saw him.

80
00:07:20,470 --> 00:07:22,769
But seeing his actions,

81
00:07:22,769 --> 00:07:24,309
I think he is ambitious.

82
00:07:24,309 --> 00:07:28,269
If he turns to the south, it would be too late.

83
00:07:28,269 --> 00:07:29,569
Official Li,

84
00:07:29,569 --> 00:07:32,270
