85
00:07:32,270 --> 00:07:34,149
You said that out of your own imagination?

86
00:07:34,149 --> 00:07:37,270
What if we lose?

87
00:07:37,270 --> 00:07:39,449
Please send our ambassadors

88
00:07:39,449 --> 00:07:41,889
- to make an agreement with the Jing Empire.
- Agreement?

89
00:07:41,889 --> 00:07:44,390
Prime Minister was forced to make that with the Liang Empire.

90
00:07:44,390 --> 00:07:46,449
We had more tribute. People are miserable.

91
00:07:46,449 --> 00:07:48,810
If we do as before,

92
00:07:48,810 --> 00:07:53,110
should we always do like that?

93
00:07:53,110 --> 00:07:55,370
Speaking of Prime Minister Qin,

94
00:07:55,370 --> 00:07:58,149
I am reminded of him.

95
00:07:59,330 --> 00:08:01,470
Why didn't he come back?

96
00:08:01,470 --> 00:08:05,109
I called him to come back

97
00:08:05,109 --> 00:08:07,429
more than a month ago.

98
00:08:07,429 --> 00:08:09,489
Where is he?

99
00:08:09,489 --> 00:08:12,650
He has set off.

100
00:08:12,650 --> 00:08:15,229
He will soon arrive.

101
00:08:17,090 --> 00:08:18,790
I am tired.

102
00:08:18,790 --> 00:08:22,790
I will consider attacking the north.

103
00:08:22,790 --> 00:08:26,029
As for the tribute to the Liang Empire,

104
00:08:26,029 --> 00:08:28,530
we will just delay it.

105
00:08:29,570 --> 00:08:31,730
Imperial Court over!

106
00:08:32,889 --> 00:08:38,269
Long live the Emperor!

107
00:08:43,609 --> 00:08:45,309
Grand Master.
[Grand Master of the Wu Dynasty: He Yuan Chang]

108
00:08:46,090 --> 00:08:47,209
Grand Master.

109
00:08:47,209 --> 00:08:49,149
You are fishing again.

110
00:08:49,149 --> 00:08:50,869
This is His Majesty's fish.

111
00:08:50,869 --> 00:08:53,849
Only you dare to fish.

112
00:09:08,530 --> 00:09:10,430
Give it to me.

113
00:09:10,430 --> 00:09:12,730
You freed it?

114
00:09:12,730 --> 00:09:15,209
Don't pretend to be polite.

115
00:09:15,729 --> 00:09:18,730
Bad news first.

116
00:09:21,009 --> 00:09:22,990
Our business is ruined.

117
00:09:22,990 --> 00:09:27,189
His Majesty stopped tribute to Liang.

118
00:09:27,189 --> 00:09:29,149
What's the good news then?

119
00:09:29,149 --> 00:09:31,649
There's... There's no good news.

120
00:09:31,649 --> 00:09:33,310
Another piece of bad news is that

121
00:09:33,310 --> 00:09:35,469
Qin Si Yuan is coming back.

122
00:09:35,469 --> 00:09:39,230
Grand Master, what should we do?

123
00:09:40,670 --> 00:09:42,850
- Greetings, Grand Master.
- Greetings, Minister.
[Wu Dynasty's Martial Advisor: Song Xian and Transport Commissioner Han De Cheng]

124
00:09:42,850 --> 00:09:45,530
Greetings, Minister Liang.

125
00:09:46,109 --> 00:09:48,049
You can forego the formalities.

126
00:09:48,929 --> 00:09:52,609
Today I called you two

127
00:09:53,130 --> 00:09:55,669
for our tribute.

128
00:09:55,669 --> 00:09:59,289
Tomorrow, you will set off to Jiangning

129
00:09:59,289 --> 00:10:01,129
to find new suppliers.

130
00:10:02,410 --> 00:10:05,149
Order 500,000 bolts of cloth.

131
00:10:05,149 --> 00:10:07,169
Wait, wait.

132
00:10:07,169 --> 00:10:09,989
Minister, didn't we stop the tribute?

133
00:10:09,989 --> 00:10:15,489
If you allow me to guess, the tribute isn't for Liang but for Jing.

134
00:10:19,409 --> 00:10:22,690
Lord Jiang, you know less

135
00:10:22,690 --> 00:10:26,830
than a martial supervisor.

136
00:10:30,089 --> 00:10:31,989
Thank you, Grand Master.

137
00:10:36,530 --> 00:10:39,089
Grand Master, it's reckless.

138
00:10:39,089 --> 00:10:42,150
Please give it a second thought.

139
00:10:52,650 --> 00:10:55,130
Why did you free it again?

140
00:10:56,630 --> 00:10:58,430
I came to fish for the fun of it,

141
00:10:59,070 --> 00:11:01,310
not for the fish itself.

142
00:11:01,970 --> 00:11:04,349
You will understand in the future.

143
00:11:04,349 --> 00:11:08,500
[Jiangning]

144
00:11:08,500 --> 00:11:11,290
[Su Manor]

145
00:11:21,450 --> 00:11:24,330
Anyway, this is what I thought.

146
00:11:24,330 --> 00:11:27,090
I lost the Letter of Divorce anyway,

147
00:11:27,090 --> 00:11:29,150
