00:11:38,888 --> 00:11:41,889
The most important thing is I don't eat too much. And I...

153
00:12:00,269 --> 00:12:04,848
Desert. Smoke. Setting sun. The air seemed to twist.

154
00:12:04,848 --> 00:12:09,550
In the shadows, a killer got near him.

155
00:12:09,550 --> 00:12:13,569
He took out his sword to defend.

156
00:12:13,569 --> 00:12:16,190
Suddenly she kissed me and did nothing.

157
00:12:17,889 --> 00:12:20,509
Why are you peeking at my unpublished masterpiece.

158
00:12:20,509 --> 00:12:22,628
No. Young Master,

159
00:12:22,628 --> 00:12:24,860
your novel

160
00:12:24,860 --> 00:12:26,620
makes me so confused.

161
00:12:26,629 --> 00:12:29,069
It changes so abruptly.

162
00:12:29,069 --> 00:12:32,169
At one second he is to be killed. At the next second he is kissed.

163
00:12:32,169 --> 00:12:35,209
Then nothing happened. What do you mean?

164
00:12:35,209 --> 00:12:40,409
You ask me? It just happened.

165
00:12:46,050 --> 00:12:48,150
Lao Geng,

166
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:51,109
since you read love stories,

167
00:12:51,109 --> 00:12:53,429
do you have a lover?

168
00:12:53,429 --> 00:12:57,690
Young Master, how can you ask me that?

169
00:13:10,029 --> 00:13:13,409
Please help me.

170
00:13:13,409 --> 00:13:15,990
I have a friend.

171
00:13:15,990 --> 00:13:20,829
One day, without any hint,

172
00:13:20,829 --> 00:13:22,769
his wife kissed him.

173
00:13:22,769 --> 00:13:24,549
Your wife kissed you?

174
00:13:24,549 --> 00:13:27,329
My friend! Friend.

175
00:13:27,329 --> 00:13:30,649
Actually, it's quite easy to guess the reason.

176
00:13:30,649 --> 00:13:33,909
You... Oh no, your "friend,"

177
00:13:33,909 --> 00:13:36,709
must have hid his private money.

178
00:13:36,709 --> 00:13:38,148
Let me tell you guys.

179
00:13:38,148 --> 00:13:41,208
Every time my wife treats me well,

180
00:13:41,209 --> 00:13:43,969
I must have done something wrong.

181
00:13:43,969 --> 00:13:47,829
She is asking me in this implied way.

182
00:13:47,829 --> 00:13:50,049
If I don't tell the truth,

183
00:13:50,049 --> 00:13:54,689
she will beat me to death.

184
00:13:54,689 --> 00:13:57,830
But this is common at my home.

185
00:13:57,830 --> 00:13:59,968
If she kisses you from time to time, there's no need to worry.

186
00:13:59,969 --> 00:14:01,190
No.

187
00:14:01,190 --> 00:14:05,670
- She must be guilty if she cares about you.
- What?

188
00:14:05,670 --> 00:14:10,388
Only when she marries a concubine will she kiss me.

189
00:14:10,388 --> 00:14:14,509
Your friend's wife wants a concubine.

190
00:14:14,509 --> 00:14:15,829
She is your wife.

191
00:14:15,829 --> 00:14:18,888
If she has a concubine, then you can be brothers. Right?

192
00:14:18,888 --> 00:14:21,869
Feng Yuan, nonsense!

193
00:14:21,869 --> 00:14:24,869
Ning Yi is so good. How can his wife want a concubine?

194
00:14:24,869 --> 00:14:28,308
Nonsense? A matrilocal husband always listens to his wife.

195
00:14:28,308 --> 00:14:29,550
What's wrong with a concubine?

196
00:14:29,550 --> 00:14:31,410
Always listens to his wife? You are so rigid.

197
00:14:31,410 --> 00:14:33,929
- You stick to the old rules.
- You aren't flexible!

198
00:14:33,929 --> 00:14:35,448
That's not for sure.

199
00:14:35,449 --> 00:14:36,629
I have a friend.

200
00:14:36,629 --> 00:14:40,709
He was sent to the school and his wife had a concubine at home.

201
00:14:40,709 --> 00:14:41,850
You see?

202
00:14:41,850 --> 00:14:44,888
You are illogical. You just see part of it.

203
00:14:44,888 --> 00:14:47,030
You are...

204
00:14:48,009 --> 00:14:49,609
Where is Ning Yi?

205
00:14:53,569 --> 00:14:57,188
- Is this the dress that was at the Jade Garden Poetry Meeting?
- Yes.

206
00:14:57,188 --> 00:14:59,730
Do you know how to match it?

207
00:15:01,890 --> 00:15:03,650
- It…
- Excuse me, dear customer.

208
00:15:03,650 --> 00:15:05,449
The one of Moon Silk is perfect with Cloud Gauze,

209
00:15:05,449 --> 00:15:07,589
but it's better to be made of Cloud Silk.

210
00:15:07,589 --> 00:15:10,810
We have a sample there. Please have a look.

211
00:15:10,810 --> 00:15:12,369
Please.

212
00:15:13,590 --> 00:15:14,869
Shopkeeper..

213
00:15:14,869 --> 00:15:17,968
Young Master Ning left a training guidebook

214
00:15:17,968 --> 00:15:20,609
which writes the way to treat customers.

215
00:15:20,609 --> 00:15:21,889
Have a look.

216
00:15:21,889 --> 00:15:25,448
Our shop is moving ahead. We have to keep up with it.

217
00:15:25,448 --> 00:15:27,968
Hey, you. What?

218
00:15:27,968 --> 00:15:30,129
You think you can despise me?

219
00:15:30,129 --> 00:15:31,849
Do you think you're going to be the new shop keeper?

220
00:15:31,850 --> 00:15:33,849
No. No. I…

221
00:15:33,849 --> 00:15:35,470
What happened?

222
00:15:35,470 --> 00:15:37,969
- Boss, nothing.
- Boss.

223
00:15:38,970 --> 00:15:42,270
- Young Master.
- Young Master.

224
00:15:51,789 --> 00:15:55,189
I didn't want to come.

225
00:15:56,750 --> 00:16:00,250
I was playing with my classmates.

226
00:16:05,190 --> 00:16:08,269
How is the business going?

227
00:16:08,269 --> 00:16:10,069
Good. Good.

228
00:16:10,069 --> 00:16:14,030
After the poetry meeting, all girls in Jiangning want the Moon Silk.

229
00:16:14,030 --> 00:16:17,708
Su's Cloth Shop is completely famous in the city.

230
00:16:17,708 --> 00:16:20,190
Thanks to you and Boss.

231
00:16:20,190 --> 00:16:22,649
I have nothing to do with it.

232
00:16:23,630 --> 00:16:27,569
Boss is the one to be praised.

233
00:16:31,610 --> 00:16:33,609
I appreciate your efforts.

234
00:16:33,609 --> 00:16:36,230
You can get one piece of Moon Silk

235
00:16:36,230 --> 00:16:39,809
for your wives or daughters.

236
00:16:39,809 --> 00:16:42,390
He hasn't been married.

237
00:16:42,390 --> 00:16:43,990
What are you saying?

238
00:16:43,990 --> 00:16:46,808
Even if you're not married, you must have someone you love, right?

239
00:16:46,808 --> 00:16:51,409
Give her that and she will know your feelings.

240
00:16:51,409 --> 00:16:54,889
A fair lady is the desire of a gentleman.

241
00:16:54,889 --> 00:16:58,569
If you don't tell her, how can she know that?

242
00:17:00,730 --> 00:17:02,130
Right?

243
00:17:02,130 --> 00:17:04,170
Yes, yes.

244
00:17:04,170 --> 00:17:05,809
Go on.

245
00:17:27,689 --> 00:17:29,689
What?

246
00:18:27,050 --> 00:18:28,328
Anyone coming?

247
00:18:28,329 --> 00:18:30,329
Coming.

248
00:18:32,090 --> 00:18:35,909
Young Master Wu, how can I help you?

249
00:18:41,809 --> 00:18:44,030
Thank you.

250
00:18:45,769 --> 00:18:48,250
If you sing that again,

251
00:18:48,250 --> 00:18:51,089
I will smash your shop.

252
00:18:52,810 --> 00:18:54,910
Change the song.

253
00:18:55,850 --> 00:18:57,450
Yes, Young Master Wu.

254
00:18:57,450 --> 00:18:59,350
Go now.

255
00:19:06,869 --> 00:19:09,089
You are easy

256
00:19:09,810 --> 00:19:11,710
to get angry.

257
00:19:14,430 --> 00:19:18,630
Ning Yi is powerful in the Su Family.

258
00:19:18,630 --> 00:19:22,509
You may not be happy.

259
00:19:23,410 --> 00:19:26,430
He showed himself at the meeting.

260
00:19:26,430 --> 00:19:30,570
You did nothing as the shopkeeper.

261
00:19:30,570 --> 00:19:33,170
Even if you want to stay here,

262
00:19:33,170 --> 00:19:35,849
they will not accept you.

263
00:19:37,430 --> 00:19:39,790
You mean…

264
00:19:41,650 --> 00:19:43,290
When will Commandant Song come?

265
00:19:43,290 --> 00:19:47,650
According to the letter, he will arrive before night.

266
00:19:48,989 --> 00:19:52,909
We will have an important guest tonight.

267
00:19:52,909 --> 00:19:56,250
If you are interested,

268
00:19:56,250 --> 00:19:59,109
you can join in the business.

269
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:01,800
Instead of being kicked out,

270
00:20:01,809 --> 00:20:06,909
you may choose another master.

271
00:20:14,169 --> 00:20:16,369
- Young Master Ning.
- Young Master Ning.

272
00:20:16,369 --> 00:20:19,689
Miss Yuan, why are you here?

273
00:20:19,689 --> 00:20:21,949
You know my sister?

274
00:20:21,949 --> 00:20:24,089
Miss Nie is your sister?

275
00:20:24,089 --> 00:20:26,189
Of course.

276
00:20:26,189 --> 00:20:29,248
At the poetry meeting, she helped me a lot.

277
00:20:29,248 --> 00:20:32,089
I came to thank her.

278
00:20:32,089 --> 00:20:34,709
Young Master Ning, would you like to have a try?

279
00:20:34,709 --> 00:20:38,949
Yes. Great. I am really hungry.

280
00:20:38,949 --> 00:20:42,549
If it is made by you, it must be tasty. It must be delicious.

281
00:20:42,549 --> 00:20:44,709
How is business going?

282
00:20:49,089 --> 00:20:53,069
If it is not so good, that's all right.

283
00:21:12,969 --> 00:21:19,569
Actually, it's not so bad.

284
00:21:20,949 --> 00:21:26,469
If a person is extremely hungry,

285
00:21:27,170 --> 00:21:29,569
he would like to eat it.

286
00:21:29,569 --> 00:21:33,110
You may sell it beside the dessert.

287
00:21:36,769 --> 00:21:38,369
No.

288
00:21:39,510 --> 00:21:41,789
The pancake.

289
00:21:41,789 --> 00:21:43,808
How did you make it?

290
00:21:43,808 --> 00:21:48,409
How many pancakes did you sell?

291
00:21:48,409 --> 00:21:50,570
It's the first one.

292
00:21:54,589 --> 00:21:59,289
Okay. You helped me before.

293
00:21:59,289 --> 00:22:02,529
I will give you an idea.

294
00:22:03,709 --> 00:22:06,768
For example, you can sell preserved eggs.

295
00:22:06,768 --> 00:22:09,810
- What?
- Preserved eggs?

296
00:22:17,949 --> 00:22:22,268
Come on. It is the menu of preserved eggs.

297
00:22:22,268 --> 00:22:24,688
You can have a try. It's simple.

298
00:22:24,688 --> 00:22:29,129
If you don't understand, just remember it is made of duck eggs.

299
00:22:29,129 --> 00:22:31,088
The products of eggs. That's enough.

300
00:22:31,088 --> 00:22:33,830
It's easy and profitable.

301
00:22:33,830 --> 00:22:37,450
- Thank you then.
- You are welcome.

302
00:22:37,450 --> 00:22:41,590
[Jiangning City outskirts]

303
00:22:51,989 --> 00:22:54,110
Commissioner Han.

304
00:22:54,110 --> 00:22:56,169
Stop. Stop.

305
00:22:56,169 --> 00:22:57,670
Stop.

306
00:22:58,650 --> 00:22:59,810
Why?

307
00:22:59,810 --> 00:23:02,169
How far is it to Jiangning?

308
00:23:02,169 --> 00:23:04,669
I was about to tell you. Only 15km to go.

309
00:23:04,669 --> 00:23:07,010
We will arrive in the afternoon.

310
00:23:11,010 --> 00:23:16,049
When we arrive, we will go to the Wu Family to discuss about the order.

311
00:23:16,049 --> 00:23:18,570
You don't have to go with me.

312
00:23:19,349 --> 00:23:23,489
Grand Master didn't ask us to go to the Lou Family in Lin'an.

313
00:23:23,489 --> 00:23:27,549
Instead, we were asked to come here for new suppliers.

314
00:23:27,549 --> 00:23:30,590
He wants a new price.

315
00:23:30,590 --> 00:23:34,830
- I think you understand the situation.
- Yes, I understand.

316
00:23:34,830 --> 00:23:36,808
Grand Master wants 500,000 bolts.

317
00:23:36,809 --> 00:23:41,550
Tributary cloth will not rot. We need it every year.

318
00:23:41,550 --> 00:23:44,670
You may find stores you are familiar with.

319
00:23:44,670 --> 00:23:47,250
We can earn money together.

320
00:23:48,190 --> 00:23:50,040
Good.

321
00:23:50,040 --> 00:23:51,750
[Lu Hong Ti]

322
00:23:51,750 --> 00:23:53,749
Let's go.

323
00:24:01,530 --> 00:24:04,550
Can't you let me win?

324
00:24:06,650 --> 00:24:08,750
Wonderful.

325
00:24:08,750 --> 00:24:12,968
Master Qin's chess shows the atmosphere of war.

326
00:24:12,969 --> 00:24:16,629
It's not like playing chess but like a war.

327
00:24:16,629 --> 00:24:19,969
What war?

328
00:24:19,969 --> 00:24:24,049
I just bet with him.

329
00:24:24,049 --> 00:24:28,409
Who loses should buy the winner a dinner.

330
00:24:28,409 --> 00:24:32,069
I didn't expect the bet made him serious.

331
00:24:32,069 --> 00:24:33,409
That's good.

332
00:24:33,409 --> 00:24:35,949
Master Kang, let's have a bet.

333
00:24:35,949 --> 00:24:39,788
What will you bet? The loser would get the chair. Shall we?

334
00:24:39,788 --> 00:24:43,488
Master Kang, you are the emperor's son-in-law. You should be merciful.

335
00:24:43,488 --> 00:24:48,749
No. You always ask me to get the chair. Can't you get it once?

336
00:24:48,749 --> 00:24:50,410
What's wrong with my identity?

337
00:24:50,410 --> 00:24:54,288
You are the most famous poet in Jiangning.

338
00:24:54,288 --> 00:24:57,509
Do you still have time to watch us playing?

339
00:24:57,509 --> 00:24:59,689
Don't tease me.

340
00:24:59,689 --> 00:25:02,368
I am not a poet. I can't write poems.

341
00:25:02,368 --> 00:25:06,908
It's the work of Mr. Su. I just borrow it.

342
00:25:06,908 --> 00:25:08,849
Mr. Su?

343
00:25:08,849 --> 00:25:10,928
I really can't write poetry.

344
00:25:10,929 --> 00:25:14,350
If you want me to write, it would be like this.

345
00:25:14,350 --> 00:25:17,668
There is a beauty in the north. She hanged herself on the tree.

346
00:25:17,668 --> 00:25:21,148
If you love each other, just hang yourselves on the tree.

347
00:25:21,148 --> 00:25:24,988
Great people are always lonely. They should all hang themselves on the tree.

348
00:25:24,988 --> 00:25:27,609
Why did you make it to where everyone hung themselves?

349
00:25:27,610 --> 00:25:33,328
I can't write poems. I might as well hang myself on the tree.

350
00:25:35,460 --> 00:25:39,770
[Wu Manor]

351
00:25:50,350 --> 00:25:53,269
- You arrived, Commandant Song.
- Boss Wu.

352
00:25:53,269 --> 00:25:55,609
- You must be tired.
- Be careful. Let me help you.

353
00:25:55,609 --> 00:25:57,609
You don't have to. It's okay for me to walk.

354
00:25:57,609 --> 00:25:59,569
My pleasure. This way please.

355
00:25:59,569 --> 00:26:02,330
- Let's discuss inside.
- Okay, okay. How was your journey?

356
00:26:02,330 --> 00:26:04,909
It was quite fine.

357
00:26:04,909 --> 00:26:09,668
In your letter, you mentioned something important.

358
00:26:09,668 --> 00:26:14,049
I think I may not understand you.

359
00:26:18,129 --> 00:26:20,029
Please.

360
00:26:20,029 --> 00:26:24,128
During the war between Liang and Jing, Liang is going to lose.

361
00:26:24,128 --> 00:26:29,148
In Grand Master's opinion, we may prepare more tribute for the Jing Empire.

362
00:26:29,148 --> 00:26:35,630
So I have to mind the business of the tribute.

363
00:26:39,189 --> 00:26:41,930
So you mean…

364
00:26:41,930 --> 00:26:45,068
I understand your capability.

365
00:26:45,068 --> 00:26:47,728
You may start to buy silk,

366
00:26:47,728 --> 00:26:51,888
and I will buy your cloth after it is determined.

367
00:26:51,888 --> 00:26:57,108
Everyone wants the order. Only the one with capability can.

368
00:26:57,108 --> 00:27:00,690
What do you think?

369
00:27:01,369 --> 00:27:02,989
Of course.

370
00:27:02,989 --> 00:27:06,790
I will appreciate your help.

371
00:27:06,790 --> 00:27:12,168
If I can get the order, I will pay you.

372
00:27:12,168 --> 00:27:17,870
I will give you secret commission only known between us.

373
00:27:21,009 --> 00:27:26,229
Commissioner Han came with you. Where is he?

374
00:27:26,229 --> 00:27:29,209
He has somewhere to go.

375
00:27:30,570 --> 00:27:32,748
- Serve Commandant. Hurry up.
- Come on, Commandant Song.

376
00:27:32,748 --> 00:27:35,070
Cheers.

377
00:27:35,070 --> 00:27:36,650
Please.

378
00:27:41,969 --> 00:27:44,069
Is this the carriage?

379
00:27:56,410 --> 00:27:58,169
- Brother-in-law.
- Lao Su.

380
00:27:58,169 --> 00:28:00,648
Uncle, I miss you so much.

381
00:28:00,648 --> 00:28:03,109
You must be Wenxing. You have grown up.

382
00:28:03,109 --> 00:28:06,869
I wouldn't recognize you on the street.

383
00:28:06,869 --> 00:28:09,709
You must be tired. Please come in.

384
00:28:09,709 --> 00:28:11,869
- Please.
- Right, come.

385
00:28:14,050 --> 00:28:18,368
Uncle, why didn't tell us that you would come?

386
00:28:18,368 --> 00:28:22,249
We can have a party for you.

387
00:28:22,249 --> 00:28:25,829
Your uncle just came to us and meet outside of the manor.

388
00:28:25,829 --> 00:28:28,630
He must have his reasons.

389
00:28:28,630 --> 00:28:29,968
Your father is right.

390
00:28:29,968 --> 00:28:35,309
This time I came with good news.

391
00:28:35,309 --> 00:28:37,390
What is it?

392
00:28:37,390 --> 00:28:41,688
Silk sold in the south bank of the river must have belonged to the Wu Family.

393
00:28:41,688 --> 00:28:45,309
You must now buy silk in the north bank.

394
00:28:45,309 --> 00:28:47,569
The more, the better.

395
00:28:49,630 --> 00:28:51,950
Why?

396
00:28:51,950 --> 00:28:55,189
Lao Su, do you know about the war?

397
00:28:57,310 --> 00:28:59,530
The war?

398
00:28:59,530 --> 00:29:02,989
Everyone knows that the Liang Empire is going to lose.

399
00:29:02,989 --> 00:29:04,109
Yes.

400
00:29:04,109 --> 00:29:07,649
Then our agreement with Liang is to be canceled.

401
00:29:07,649 --> 00:29:13,209
We will make a new agreement with Jing. What will happen next?

402
00:29:13,209 --> 00:29:16,449
We need more tribute.

403
00:29:16,449 --> 00:29:19,030
- Then the tributary cloth...
- Exactly.

404
00:29:19,030 --> 00:29:22,768
Song Xian, our Commandant Song also came to Jiangning.

405
00:29:22,768 --> 00:29:24,729
He discussed this with the Wu Family,

406
00:29:24,729 --> 00:29:29,328
while I will help my families.

407
00:29:29,328 --> 00:29:32,089
I am now the transport commissioner.

408
00:29:32,089 --> 00:29:34,269
- I still have quite some skills.
- Yes.

409
00:29:34,269 --> 00:29:37,329
Then we would need more cloth for tribute.

410
00:29:37,329 --> 00:29:40,010
You just buy silk and make cloth.

411
00:29:40,010 --> 00:29:43,430
Let's take the order of the government.

412
00:29:43,430 --> 00:29:47,970
Really? That's great.

413
00:29:47,970 --> 00:29:52,989
However, Su Tan'er, your cousin is not easy to deal with.

414
00:29:52,989 --> 00:29:54,969
You should be careful.

415
00:29:54,969 --> 00:29:57,188
We are family.

416
00:29:57,188 --> 00:29:58,549
Yes.

417
00:29:58,549 --> 00:30:01,029
Yes. Brother-in-law,

418
00:30:01,089 --> 00:30:03,928
As for the price...

419
00:30:04,000 --> 00:30:06,800
Don't worry about the price.

420
00:30:06,800 --> 00:30:08,300
Jing is different from Liang.

421
00:30:08,300 --> 00:30:10,200
Just treat it casually.

422
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:12,800
I said we need more cloth.

423
00:30:12,800 --> 00:30:16,400
The government is going to pay more.

424
00:30:19,600 --> 00:30:22,400
Come on. Uncle, cheers!

425
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:24,300
- Brother-in-law.
- Uncle.

426
00:30:33,600 --> 00:30:36,800
Do as I said this afternoon.

427
00:30:36,800 --> 00:30:37,800
It's important.

428
00:30:37,800 --> 00:30:39,400
I will.

429
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:41,400
Thank you.

430
00:30:41,400 --> 00:30:42,800
Don't worry.

431
00:30:42,800 --> 00:30:44,800
You don't have to see me off.

432
00:30:44,800 --> 00:30:46,200
Let's go.

433
00:30:55,200 --> 00:30:57,400
Miss, there's a letter from Lin'an.

434
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:59,400
- Is it from Shuwan?
- Yes.

435
00:30:59,400 --> 00:31:02,800
By the way, Miss, Commissioner Han will arrive tonight.

436
00:31:02,800 --> 00:31:04,400
We will have a party for him.

437
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:06,500
We will have dinner together.

438
00:31:06,500 --> 00:31:09,200
Uncle? Why did he come at this time?

439
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:10,400
Yes.

440
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:12,400
It is the season of tribute.

441
00:31:12,400 --> 00:31:15,400
He should be in the capital and mind it.

442
00:31:15,400 --> 00:31:17,200
He shouldn't be in Jiangning.

443
00:31:17,200 --> 00:31:20,000
Oh right, I heard Song Xian or Commandant Song also came.

444
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:22,500
They came together.

445
00:31:25,800 --> 00:31:29,900
[Letter]

446
00:31:31,200 --> 00:31:32,600
What's wrong, Miss?

447
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:36,000
What did Miss Lou write?

448
00:31:36,800 --> 00:31:40,000
She wrote to let me ask about the tribute.

449
00:31:40,000 --> 00:31:43,000
There may not be tribute for Liang.

450
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:46,400
Jing may ask for more tribute.

451
00:31:46,400 --> 00:31:49,400
It is our business.

452
00:31:51,800 --> 00:31:54,600
The Lou Family is designated by the royals.

453
00:31:54,600 --> 00:31:57,000
It's their business.

454
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:59,100
We are not like them.

455
00:31:59,900 --> 00:32:04,400
Oh right, Miss. Does Miss Lou have any way to help you?

456
00:32:04,400 --> 00:32:07,800
If she has, and we can take part in it,

457
00:32:07,800 --> 00:32:09,800
we would be better.

458
00:32:09,800 --> 00:32:13,200
You said uncle came.

459
00:32:20,400 --> 00:32:22,600
Come on. Cheers.
[Su Manor]

460
00:32:30,900 --> 00:32:34,800
Commissioner, it's rare for you to come back.

461
00:32:34,800 --> 00:32:38,800
If you have time, you can stay longer.

462
00:32:38,800 --> 00:32:41,200
Thank you.

463
00:32:41,200 --> 00:32:42,800
I ask for a leave

464
00:32:42,800 --> 00:32:44,600
because I miss you.

465
00:32:44,600 --> 00:32:47,200
I would like to stay longer.

466
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:48,800
That's good.

467
00:32:48,800 --> 00:32:51,000
It's been years since I left.

468
00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:53,200
Something may have changed.

469
00:32:53,800 --> 00:32:55,800
For example,

470
00:32:55,800 --> 00:33:00,000
a matrilocal husband can eat with us.

471
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:01,500
If others know that,

472
00:33:01,500 --> 00:33:04,600
they would laugh at us.

473
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:08,800
Commissioner Han,

474
00:33:08,800 --> 00:33:11,200
Young Master is not an ordinary man.

475
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:13,200
He is good at business.

476
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:15,800
If it weren't for him,

477
00:33:15,800 --> 00:33:18,800
the Su Family wouldn't be as successful.

478
00:33:18,800 --> 00:33:20,000
Yes.

479
00:33:20,000 --> 00:33:21,700
I heard that,

480
00:33:21,700 --> 00:33:24,500
but he is still a matrilocal husband.

481
00:33:24,500 --> 00:33:27,800
Of course he should do that.

482
00:33:27,800 --> 00:33:30,800
The achievement is not worth mentioning.

483
00:33:32,200 --> 00:33:34,200
You hold a party for me

484
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:36,400
but I have to eat with him.

485
00:33:36,400 --> 00:33:39,400
If others know that, my name

486
00:33:39,400 --> 00:33:42,100
would be ruined.

487
00:33:43,500 --> 00:33:45,000
Uncle.

488
00:33:46,600 --> 00:33:51,000
If a single meal with me could ruin your name,

489
00:33:52,600 --> 00:33:56,300
then it seems to me that you don't have a strong name in the first place.

490
00:33:56,300 --> 00:33:57,700
You—

491
00:33:58,400 --> 00:34:02,200
Nephew-in-law, he is your uncle.

492
00:34:02,200 --> 00:34:03,400
How can you say that?

493
00:34:03,400 --> 00:34:04,400
That's right.

494
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:05,800
He is your elder.

495
00:34:05,800 --> 00:34:07,800
How dare you not respect him?

496
00:34:07,800 --> 00:34:10,900
Brother-in-law, if you respect him,

497
00:34:10,900 --> 00:34:13,800
you can regard him as your father.

498
00:34:13,800 --> 00:34:17,200
I don't have such an uncle.

499
00:34:17,800 --> 00:34:20,400
See? Am I right?

500
00:34:20,400 --> 00:34:22,800
Uncle.

501
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:25,600
Come, have more food.

502
00:34:25,600 --> 00:34:27,800
It's good for your health.

503
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:36,300
I heard we may need more tribute

504
00:34:36,300 --> 00:34:40,200
during the war.

505
00:34:40,200 --> 00:34:42,400
Did you know about it?

506
00:34:42,400 --> 00:34:43,800
Elder Master,

507
00:34:43,800 --> 00:34:45,400
it's the same as before.

508
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:47,800
We don't need more.

509
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:49,700
Come on, uncle.

510
00:35:05,200 --> 00:35:07,000
Miss, what's wrong?

511
00:35:07,000 --> 00:35:09,700
You looked upset after dinner.

512
00:35:10,900 --> 00:35:16,000
Shuwan wrote that we would need more tribute.

513
00:35:16,000 --> 00:35:19,400
Uncle said differently.

514
00:35:19,400 --> 00:35:23,600
Do you think Miss Lou cheats you?

515
00:35:25,300 --> 00:35:28,100
I'm afraid uncle has ulterior motives.

516
00:35:28,100 --> 00:35:32,600
He wants to cooperate with the Second Master's.

517
00:35:32,600 --> 00:35:34,900
You are right.

518
00:35:34,900 --> 00:35:37,100
That's what he thinks.

519
00:35:40,700 --> 00:35:44,100
Wenxing, are you ready?

520
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:45,800
Uncle, don't worry.

521
00:35:45,800 --> 00:35:49,200
I have got the order of silk in the north.

522
00:35:50,100 --> 00:35:51,800
Good.

523
00:35:55,000 --> 00:35:57,000
Thank you, Uncle.

524
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:08,000
It's a gift for you.

525
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:12,000
When we succeed, I will pay you.

526
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:14,400
Then from the beginning,

527
00:36:14,400 --> 00:36:17,600
Commissioner Han didn't want to help us.

528
00:36:17,600 --> 00:36:19,100
Yes.

529
00:36:19,100 --> 00:36:23,200
Will your Miss give commission to him?

530
00:36:23,200 --> 00:36:26,400
She just thinks her cloth is good.

531
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:28,400
Then she will get orders.

532
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:31,600
She doesn't understand things in business.

533
00:36:31,600 --> 00:36:34,000
They always think dirty,

534
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:36,000
think about their own profit.

535
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:37,500
Don't you think I should think so?

536
00:36:37,500 --> 00:36:39,600
If my cloth is better than Wenxing's,

537
00:36:39,600 --> 00:36:41,800
I should compete with him decently.

538
00:36:41,800 --> 00:36:44,800
But he already started to buy silk.

539
00:36:47,200 --> 00:36:50,200
Where else can you get silk?

540
00:36:50,200 --> 00:36:51,700
I can.

